    Kitchen-->>API: GET kitchen queue
    Kitchen-->>API: Accept order
    Kitchen-->>API: Mark ready
    API-->>Mock: POST /deliveries

    Note over API,Mock: Callback path implemented
    Mock->>API: POST delivery webhook
    API->>API: Update state/history

    Web-->>API: GET order tracking
    API-->>Web: Status timeline
